social_posts.post_text: We at jonnyknits are huge huntington library, art museum, and botanical garden stans (poppy is my membership plus one) happy spring! 🌷
New baby Bella and some little animal friends they met. 🐿️❤️‍🔥
Florida photo dump!! ^_____^ Also got a picture with Shawn mendes (2nd to last pic) 🏰🌴🐊🌞 back to knitting!

All of my knitted friends are made by me on a knitting machine. If you wanna learn about the knitting process, Discovering Machine Knitting by Kandy Diamond @knit_and_destroy is finally out! You can get a copy directly from her web store. Super excited to have been a part of this excellent resource + it has some very old pics I took in my bedroom studio lol. ❤️‍🔥
